QuestData.Title: Other Interests
QuestData.Description:
Madam Goya is interested in many unusual items other than just rare metals.
Keep an eye out for these particular items during your travels in Nazjatar.
Deliver them to me and Madam Goya will consider you for special access.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver $1oa Particularly Dense Rock to Steelsage Gao.
